Comment j'ai deteste les maths

Science Documentary hosted by Olivier Peyon, published by TV5Monde in 2013 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/9/93/Comment-j-ai-deteste-les-maths-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Many consider mathematics a subject that is boring, daunting, and abstruse. Yet its importance in society continues to grow: Apple or Google are driven by algorithms and formulas. Why do so many people dislike maths? The greatest mathematicians try to reconcile us with their subject...
